    15,                      !- February Ground Temperature {C}
    15,                      !- March Ground Temperature {C}
    16,                      !- April Ground Temperature {C}
    17,                      !- May Ground Temperature {C}
    17,                      !- June Ground Temperature {C}
    18,                      !- July Ground Temperature {C}
